text: Wagga Wagga is an electoral district of New South Wales. It was created in 1894, abolished in 1904, recreated in 1913, reabolished in 1920 and recreated in 1927. It is normally a conservative electorate. It is currently held by Joe McGirr, an independent. ==Election results== ==References== Wagga Wagga
